<title type="html"><![CDATA[5/30(Sat.)Chinese women cut their hair once in life time./The pandemic is reshaping education(Host:Cecillia)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=395&amp;p=412#p412"><![CDATA[
5/30(Sat.)Meet the Chinese women who only cut their hair once in life time./The Coronavirus pandemic is reshaping education(Cecillia)<br /><br /><br />Section 1<br /><br />Meet the Chinese women who only cut their hair once in life time.<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.vogue.com/projects/13548460/women-of-huang-luo-china-long-hair-tradition/">https://www.vogue.com/projects/13548460 ... tradition/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions <br /><br />1. How do you take care of your hair? Do you have any special hair care recipe ?<br />2. What do you think about this special “long haired” village?<br />3. Please share some special rituals that you have seen or heard?<br /><br />Section 2<br /><br />The Coronavirus pandemic is reshaping education<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://qz.com/1826369/how-coronavirus-is-changing-education/">https://qz.com/1826369/how-coronavirus- ... education/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. What are the home-environment factors that influence home schooling?<br />2. What are the technical challenges associated with home schooling?<br />3. Other than knowledge dissemination, what roles can schools play in our society?<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Wed May 27, 2020 10:04 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
